node.text:
I always feel that it is a tough and hard career to be a farmer. Our local farmers helped in contributing a small portion of daily supply fresh local produce to our supermarket and grocer retailer. During this tough period of time, I hope we can support them in return by Subscribing the “ 𝐒𝐔𝐑𝐕𝐈𝐕𝐀𝐋 𝐏𝐀𝐂𝐊 “ organised by 
https://www.facebook.com/thelocalfarmsg/
Get your fresh local produce delivered to your doorstep, 
Check out the detail of the Survival Pack ↙️
The link in the bio of @thefishfarmersg 
https://www.gardenasia.com/the-survivor-pack/

#farmtohome #thelocalfarm #farmtotable #stayhome #sgcircuitbreaker #sgcircuitbreakerhomecook #sgcircuitbreaker2020 #circuitbreakersg #stayhomecooking #sghomecooks #sghomecooking #supportlocalfarmers #supportlocalfarms #supportlocalfarms❤️ #cookingathome #grocerdelivery #grocerpack #singaporehomecooks
@rontreechan  thank you for your support and shout out for @thelocalfarmsg 🙏
@myjream not salmon, but I can’t tell what fish it is without the head 🤣🤣 it could be Barramundi or Tilapia
@rontreechan @myjream We have Red Snapper and Seabass (also known as Barramundi) fillets in the TLF Survivor Pack!
@thelocalfarmsg thank you 😊 hope raise awareness to our local farmers 😍

THank you!! so much for the shout out! hope you like the farm fresh goodness!
Stay Safe!
